, and pain or burning during urination. If a serious infection, an opportunistic infection, or sepsis develops, tofacitinib should be interrupted until the infection is controlled.', 'Others', NULL, NULL, 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/33447/', '[1] "Product Information. Xeljanz (tofacitinib)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals Group, New York, NY.', 1767365203);
